{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"You may not know this,"},{"time":2000,"text":"but you are celebrating an anniversary with me."},{"time":5000,"text":"I'm not married,"},{"time":8000,"text":"but one year ago today,"},{"time":11000,"text":"I woke up"},{"time":13000,"text":"from a month-long coma,"},{"time":16000,"text":"following a double lung transplant."},{"time":20000,"text":"Crazy, I know. Insane."},{"time":25000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":27000,"text":"Six years before that,"},{"time":30000,"text":"I was starting my career"},{"time":32000,"text":"as an opera singer in Europe,"},{"time":34000,"text":"when I was diagnosed with"},{"time":36000,"text":"idiopathic pulmonary hypertension --"},{"time":39000,"text":"also known as PH."},{"time":41000,"text":"It happens when there's a thickening"},{"time":44000,"text":"in the pulmonary veins,"},{"time":46000,"text":"making the right side of the heart"},{"time":48000,"text":"work overtime,"},{"time":50000,"text":"and causing what I call"},{"time":52000,"text":"the reverse-Grinch effect."},{"time":54000,"text":"My heart was three-and-a-half sizes"},{"time":56000,"text":"too big."},{"time":59000,"text":"Physical activity becomes very difficult"},{"time":61000,"text":"for people with this condition,"},{"time":64000,"text":"and usually after two to five years,"},{"time":67000,"text":"you die."},{"time":69000,"text":"I went to see this specialist,"},{"time":71000,"text":"and she was top-of-the-field"},{"time":73000,"text":"and told me I had to stop singing."},{"time":76000,"text":"She said, \"Those high notes are going to kill you.\""},{"time":79000,"text":"While she didn't have any medical evidence"},{"time":81000,"text":"to back up her claim"},{"time":83000,"text":"that there was a relationship"},{"time":85000,"text":"between operatic arias"},{"time":87000,"text":"and pulmonary hypertension,"},{"time":89000,"text":"she was absolutely emphatic"},{"time":91000,"text":"I was singing my own obituary."},{"time":95000,"text":"I was very limited by my condition, physically."},{"time":98000,"text":"But I was not limited when I sang,"},{"time":101000,"text":"and as air came up from my lungs,"},{"time":103000,"text":"through my vocal cords"},{"time":105000,"text":"and passed my lips as sound,"},{"time":108000,"text":"it was the closest thing I had ever come"},{"time":111000,"text":"to transcendence."},{"time":115000,"text":"And just because of someone's hunch,"},{"time":117000,"text":"I wasn't going to give it up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":120000,"text":"Thankfully, I met Reda Girgis,"},{"time":123000,"text":"who is dry as toast,"},{"time":125000,"text":"but he and his team at Johns Hopkins"},{"time":128000,"text":"didn't just want me to survive,"},{"time":130000,"text":"they wanted me"},{"time":132000,"text":"to live a meaningful life."},{"time":135000,"text":"This meant making trade-offs."},{"time":138000,"text":"I come from Colorado."},{"time":140000,"text":"It's a mile high,"},{"time":142000,"text":"and I grew up there with my 10 brothers and sisters"},{"time":145000,"text":"and two adoring parents."},{"time":147000,"text":"Well, the altitude exacerbated my symptoms."},{"time":150000,"text":"So I moved to Baltimore to be near my doctors"},{"time":152000,"text":"and enrolled in a conservatory nearby."},{"time":156000,"text":"I couldn't walk as much as I used to,"},{"time":158000,"text":"so I opted for five-inch heels."},{"time":161000,"text":"And I gave up salt,"},{"time":163000,"text":"I went vegan,"},{"time":165000,"text":"and I started taking huge doses of"},{"time":169000,"text":"sildenafil,"},{"time":171000,"text":"also known as Viagra."}]},{"cues":[{"time":174000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":180000,"text":"My father and my grandfather were always looking for the newest thing"},{"time":183000,"text":"in alternative or traditional therapies"},{"time":185000,"text":"for PH,"},{"time":187000,"text":"but after six months,"},{"time":189000,"text":"I couldn't walk up a small hill. I couldn't climb a flight of stairs."},{"time":192000,"text":"I could barely stand up"},{"time":194000,"text":"without feeling like I was going to faint."},{"time":196000,"text":"I had a heart catheterization,"},{"time":198000,"text":"where they measure this internal arterial pulmonary pressure,"},{"time":201000,"text":"which is supposed to be between 15 and 20."},{"time":204000,"text":"Mine was 146."},{"time":207000,"text":"I like to do things big,"},{"time":210000,"text":"and it meant one thing:"},{"time":212000,"text":"there is a big gun treatment"},{"time":214000,"text":"for pulmonary hypertension called Flolan,"},{"time":217000,"text":"and it's not just a drug;"},{"time":219000,"text":"it's a way of life."},{"time":221000,"text":"Doctors insert a catheter into your chest,"},{"time":224000,"text":"which is attached to a pump"},{"time":226000,"text":"that weighs about four-and-a-half pounds."},{"time":230000,"text":"Every day, 24 hours, that pump is at your side,"},{"time":233000,"text":"administering medicine"},{"time":235000,"text":"directly to your heart,"},{"time":238000,"text":"and it's not"},{"time":240000,"text":"a particularly preferable"},{"time":243000,"text":"medicine in many senses."},{"time":245000,"text":"This is a list of the side effects:"},{"time":248000,"text":"if you eat too much salt,"},{"time":251000,"text":"like a peanut butter and jelly sandwich,"},{"time":253000,"text":"you'll probably end up in the ICU."},{"time":256000,"text":"If you go through a metal detector,"},{"time":258000,"text":"you'll probably die."},{"time":260000,"text":"If you get a bubble in your medicine --"},{"time":263000,"text":"because you have to mix it every morning --"},{"time":265000,"text":"and it stays in there,"},{"time":267000,"text":"you probably die."},{"time":269000,"text":"If you run out of medicine, you definitely die."}]},{"cues":[{"time":272000,"text":"No one wants to go on Flolan."},{"time":274000,"text":"But when I needed it,"},{"time":277000,"text":"it was a godsend."},{"time":281000,"text":"Within a few days, I could walk again."},{"time":284000,"text":"Within a few weeks, I was performing,"},{"time":287000,"text":"and in a few months,"},{"time":289000,"text":"I debuted at the Kennedy Center."},{"time":292000,"text":"The pump was a little bit problematic when performing,"},{"time":296000,"text":"so I'd attach it to my inner thigh"},{"time":298000,"text":"with the help of the girdle and an ACE bandage."},{"time":301000,"text":"Literally hundreds of elevator rides"},{"time":303000,"text":"were spent with me alone"},{"time":305000,"text":"stuffing the pump into my Spanx,"},{"time":308000,"text":"hoping the doors wouldn't open unexpectedly."},{"time":313000,"text":"And the tubing coming out of my chest"},{"time":316000,"text":"was a nightmare for costume designers."},{"time":319000,"text":"I graduated from graduate school in 2006,"},{"time":322000,"text":"and I got a fellowship to go back to Europe."},{"time":325000,"text":"A few days after arriving,"},{"time":327000,"text":"I met this wonderful, old conductor"},{"time":329000,"text":"who started casting me in all of these roles."},{"time":331000,"text":"And before long, I was commuting"},{"time":333000,"text":"between Budapest, Milan"},{"time":335000,"text":"and Florence."},{"time":337000,"text":"Though I was attached"},{"time":339000,"text":"to this ugly, unwanted,"},{"time":341000,"text":"high-maintenance, mechanical pet,"},{"time":343000,"text":"my life was kind of like the happy part in an opera --"},{"time":346000,"text":"very complicated,"},{"time":348000,"text":"but in a good way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":350000,"text":"Then in February"},{"time":353000,"text":"of 2008,"},{"time":355000,"text":"my grandfather passed away."},{"time":357000,"text":"He was a big figure in all of our lives,"},{"time":359000,"text":"and we loved him very much."},{"time":363000,"text":"It certainly didn't prepare me"},{"time":365000,"text":"for what came next."},{"time":367000,"text":"Seven weeks later,"},{"time":369000,"text":"I got a call from my family."},{"time":372000,"text":"My father had been in a catastrophic car accident,"},{"time":376000,"text":"and he died."},{"time":379000,"text":"At 24, my death would have been"},{"time":381000,"text":"entirely expected."},{"time":384000,"text":"But his --"},{"time":387000,"text":"well, the only way I can articulate how it felt"},{"time":390000,"text":"was that it precipitated"},{"time":392000,"text":"my medical decline."},{"time":395000,"text":"Against my doctors' and family's wishes,"},{"time":398000,"text":"I needed to go back for the funeral."},{"time":400000,"text":"I had to say goodbye"},{"time":402000,"text":"in some way, shape or form."},{"time":405000,"text":"But soon I was showing signs of right-heart failure,"},{"time":408000,"text":"and I had to return to sea level,"},{"time":410000,"text":"doing so knowing"},{"time":412000,"text":"that I probably would never see my home again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":417000,"text":"I canceled most of my engagements that summer,"},{"time":420000,"text":"but I had one left in Tel Aviv, so I went."},{"time":424000,"text":"After one performance,"},{"time":426000,"text":"I could barely drag myself"},{"time":428000,"text":"from the stage to the taxicab."},{"time":430000,"text":"I sat down and felt the blood"},{"time":432000,"text":"rush down from my face,"},{"time":435000,"text":"and in the heat of the desert,"},{"time":438000,"text":"I was freezing cold."},{"time":440000,"text":"My fingers started turning blue,"},{"time":442000,"text":"and I was like, \"What is going on here?\""},{"time":445000,"text":"I heard my heart's valves"},{"time":447000,"text":"snapping open and closed."},{"time":449000,"text":"The cab stopped,"},{"time":451000,"text":"and I pulled my body from it"},{"time":453000,"text":"feeling each ounce of weight"},{"time":455000,"text":"as I walked to the elevator."},{"time":457000,"text":"I fell through my apartment door"},{"time":459000,"text":"and crawled to the bathroom"},{"time":461000,"text":"where I found my problem:"},{"time":463000,"text":"I had forgotten to mix in"},{"time":465000,"text":"the most important part of my medicine."},{"time":467000,"text":"I was dying,"},{"time":469000,"text":"and if I didn't mix that stuff up fast,"},{"time":471000,"text":"I would never leave that apartment alive."},{"time":474000,"text":"I started mixing,"},{"time":476000,"text":"and I felt like everything was going to fall out through one hole or another,"},{"time":479000,"text":"but I just kept on going."},{"time":481000,"text":"Finally, with the last bottle in and the last bubble out,"},{"time":483000,"text":"I attached the pump to the tubing"},{"time":485000,"text":"and lay there hoping it would kick in"},{"time":487000,"text":"soon enough."},{"time":490000,"text":"If it didn't, I'd probably see my father"},{"time":492000,"text":"sooner than I anticipated."},{"time":494000,"text":"Thankfully, in a few minutes,"},{"time":497000,"text":"I saw the signature hive-like rash"},{"time":500000,"text":"appear on my legs,"},{"time":502000,"text":"which is a side effect of the medication,"},{"time":504000,"text":"and I knew I'd be okay."}]},{"cues":[{"time":506000,"text":"We're not big on fear in my family,"},{"time":509000,"text":"but I was scared."},{"time":511000,"text":"I went back to the States,"},{"time":513000,"text":"anticipating I'd return to Europe,"},{"time":515000,"text":"but the heart catheterization"},{"time":517000,"text":"showed that I wasn't going anywhere"},{"time":520000,"text":"further that a flight-for-life from Johns Hopkins Hospital."},{"time":522000,"text":"I performed here and there,"},{"time":524000,"text":"but as my condition deteriorated,"},{"time":526000,"text":"so did my voice."},{"time":528000,"text":"My doctor wanted me to get on the list for a lung transplant."},{"time":531000,"text":"I didn't."},{"time":533000,"text":"I had two friends who had recently died"},{"time":536000,"text":"months after having very challenging surgeries."},{"time":539000,"text":"I knew another young man, though, who had PH"},{"time":542000,"text":"who died while waiting for one."},{"time":544000,"text":"I wanted to live."},{"time":546000,"text":"I thought stem cells were a good option,"},{"time":548000,"text":"but they hadn't developed to a point"},{"time":550000,"text":"where I could take advantage of them yet."},{"time":554000,"text":"I officially took a break from singing,"},{"time":556000,"text":"and I went to the Cleveland Clinic"},{"time":558000,"text":"to be reevaluated"},{"time":560000,"text":"for the third time in five years, for transplant."},{"time":563000,"text":"I was sitting there kind of unenthusiastically talking"},{"time":566000,"text":"with the head transplant surgeon,"},{"time":569000,"text":"and I asked him if I needed a transplant,"},{"time":572000,"text":"what I could do to prepare."},{"time":574000,"text":"He said, \"Be happy."},{"time":576000,"text":"A happy patient"},{"time":578000,"text":"is a healthy patient.\""},{"time":581000,"text":"It was like in one verbal swoop"},{"time":583000,"text":"he had channeled my thoughts"},{"time":585000,"text":"on life and medicine"},{"time":587000,"text":"and Confucius."},{"time":589000,"text":"I still didn't want a transplant,"},{"time":592000,"text":"but in a month,"},{"time":594000,"text":"I was back in the hospital"},{"time":596000,"text":"with some severely edemic kankles --"},{"time":599000,"text":"very attractive."},{"time":602000,"text":"And it was right-heart failure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":606000,"text":"I finally decided"},{"time":608000,"text":"it was time to take my doctor's advice."},{"time":612000,"text":"It was time for me to go to Cleveland"},{"time":615000,"text":"and to start the agonizing wait"},{"time":618000,"text":"for a match."},{"time":620000,"text":"But the next morning,"},{"time":622000,"text":"while I was still in the hospital,"},{"time":624000,"text":"I got a telephone call."},{"time":626000,"text":"It was my doctor in Cleveland,"},{"time":628000,"text":"Marie Budev."},{"time":630000,"text":"And they had lungs."},{"time":633000,"text":"It was a match."},{"time":635000,"text":"They were from Texas."},{"time":637000,"text":"And everybody was really happy for me,"},{"time":640000,"text":"but me."},{"time":642000,"text":"Because, despite their problems,"},{"time":644000,"text":"I had spent my whole life training my lungs,"},{"time":647000,"text":"and I was not particularly enthusiastic"},{"time":649000,"text":"about giving them up."},{"time":651000,"text":"I flew to Cleveland,"},{"time":654000,"text":"and my family rushed there"},{"time":656000,"text":"in hopes that they would meet me"},{"time":658000,"text":"and say what we knew"},{"time":660000,"text":"might be our final goodbye."},{"time":662000,"text":"But organs don't wait,"},{"time":665000,"text":"and I went into surgery"},{"time":667000,"text":"before I could say goodbye."},{"time":671000,"text":"The last thing I remember"},{"time":673000,"text":"was lying on a white blanket,"},{"time":676000,"text":"telling my surgeon that I needed to see my mother again,"},{"time":679000,"text":"and to please try and save my voice."},{"time":682000,"text":"I fell into this apocalyptic dream world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":686000,"text":"During the thirteen-and-a-half-hour surgery,"},{"time":688000,"text":"I flatlined twice,"},{"time":691000,"text":"40 quarts of blood"},{"time":694000,"text":"were infused into my body."},{"time":696000,"text":"And in my surgeon's 20-year career,"},{"time":699000,"text":"he said it was among the most difficult transplants"},{"time":702000,"text":"that he's ever performed."},{"time":705000,"text":"They left my chest open for two weeks."},{"time":708000,"text":"You could see my over-sized heart"},{"time":711000,"text":"beating inside of it."},{"time":713000,"text":"I was on a dozen machines"},{"time":715000,"text":"that were keeping me alive."},{"time":717000,"text":"An infection ravaged my skin."},{"time":725000,"text":"I had hoped my voice would be saved,"},{"time":728000,"text":"but my doctors knew"},{"time":730000,"text":"that the breathing tubes going down my throat"},{"time":732000,"text":"might have already destroyed it."},{"time":734000,"text":"If they stayed in, there was no way I would ever sing again."},{"time":737000,"text":"So my doctor got the ENT,"},{"time":740000,"text":"the top guy at the clinic, to come down"},{"time":743000,"text":"and give me surgery"},{"time":745000,"text":"to move the tubes around my voice box."},{"time":749000,"text":"He said it would kill me."},{"time":751000,"text":"So my own surgeon performed the procedure"},{"time":753000,"text":"in a last-ditch attempt to save my voice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":756000,"text":"Though my mom couldn't say goodbye to me"},{"time":758000,"text":"before the surgery,"},{"time":760000,"text":"she didn't leave my side"},{"time":763000,"text":"in the months of recovery that followed."},{"time":766000,"text":"And if you want an example"},{"time":768000,"text":"of perseverance,"},{"time":770000,"text":"grit and strength"},{"time":772000,"text":"in a beautiful, little package,"},{"time":775000,"text":"it is her."},{"time":780000,"text":"One year ago"},{"time":782000,"text":"to this very day,"},{"time":785000,"text":"I woke up."},{"time":787000,"text":"I was 95 lbs."},{"time":789000,"text":"There were a dozen tubes"},{"time":791000,"text":"coming in and out of my body."},{"time":793000,"text":"I couldn't walk, I couldn't talk,"},{"time":795000,"text":"I couldn't eat, I couldn't move,"},{"time":797000,"text":"I certainly couldn't sing,"},{"time":799000,"text":"I couldn't even breathe,"},{"time":802000,"text":"but when I looked up"},{"time":805000,"text":"and I saw my mother,"},{"time":808000,"text":"I couldn't help but smile."}]},{"cues":[{"time":812000,"text":"Whether by a Mack truck"},{"time":815000,"text":"or by heart failure"},{"time":817000,"text":"or faulty lungs,"},{"time":819000,"text":"death happens."},{"time":821000,"text":"But life isn't really just about avoiding death, is it?"},{"time":825000,"text":"It's about living."},{"time":828000,"text":"Medical conditions don't negate the human condition."},{"time":832000,"text":"And when people are allowed"},{"time":834000,"text":"to pursue their passions,"},{"time":836000,"text":"doctors will find they have better,"},{"time":838000,"text":"happier and healthier patients."},{"time":840000,"text":"My parents were totally stressed out"},{"time":843000,"text":"about me going and auditioning"},{"time":845000,"text":"and traveling and performing all over the place,"},{"time":848000,"text":"but they knew that it was much better for me to do that"},{"time":850000,"text":"than be preoccupied with my own mortality all of the time."},{"time":854000,"text":"And I'm so grateful they did."}]},{"cues":[{"time":856000,"text":"This past summer, when I was running and singing"},{"time":859000,"text":"and dancing and playing with my nieces and my nephews"},{"time":862000,"text":"and my brothers and my sisters and my mother and my grandmother"},{"time":865000,"text":"in the Colorado Rockies,"},{"time":867000,"text":"I couldn't help but think of that doctor"},{"time":869000,"text":"who told me that I couldn't sing."},{"time":872000,"text":"And I wanted to tell her,"},{"time":874000,"text":"and I want to tell you,"},{"time":877000,"text":"we need to stop letting disease"},{"time":880000,"text":"divorce us from our dreams."},{"time":883000,"text":"When we do,"},{"time":885000,"text":"we will find that patients"},{"time":887000,"text":"don't just survive;"},{"time":890000,"text":"we thrive."},{"time":893000,"text":"And some of us"},{"time":895000,"text":"might even sing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":898000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":902000,"text":"[Singing: French]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1042000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":1044000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":1050000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":1052000,"text":"And I'd like to thank my pianist, Monica Lee."},{"time":1055000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":1060000,"text":"Thank you so much."},{"time":1062000,"text":"Thank you."}]}]}